item.title: Dethroning TCP From The Web?
item.description: The emergence of QUIC and HTTP3 discussing their influence on the operation of the web domain.

item.title: About me
item.description:
My name is Ahmed Al-Jabri, in recent years I completed degrees in Computer Science & Cybersecurity. My main areas of interest are Computer Systems and Networking, Distributed Systems and Secure Programming.

The intention behind this site is to share a personal blog which will cover a range of technologies, share my thoughts and present technological deep-dives on various topics of interest. You might also find posts discussing ideas and designs for some of my software projects on github.
